@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Edit Bullet Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant EditBulletCommand
participant RecordList
participant Record
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: editbullet RECORD_INDEX BULLET_INDEX / TEXT
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: EditBulletCommand
Resumake -> EditBulletCommand: execute(list)
EditBulletCommand -> RecordList: getRecord(recordIndex-1)
EditBulletCommand -> Record: editBullet(bulletIndex-1, text)
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + write if changed
@enduml
